Subject: paper 4
From: "Theodore Ming Shiuan Chao" <tc99@cornell.edu>
To: egs@cs.cornell.edu
User-Agent: SquirrelMail/1.4.5
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain;charset=iso-8859-1
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
